<h3 id="_returns" class="discrete">Returns</h3>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Situation:</strong> The order was shipped and later returned by the customer.</p>
</div>
<div class="paragraph">
<p><strong>Procedure:</strong> Book a return with the correct number of returned items/positions for the initial order. Set the return to <strong>status [9.2</strong>].</p>
</div>
